      CoriEstimator CoriEstimator.selectMixtureCombination​()
      The mixture combination strategy for selecting a posterior \(R_t\) involves finding all the estimates that have a window that is centred on the estimate date (this may involve longer windowed estimate from dates in the future) and estimating a gamma distribution with the same mean and SD as the mixture of all the estimates.
